OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA bright start on Wednesday
OL,6,Fmorning, particularly in the east.
OL,7,FTurning increasingly cloudy into the
OL,8,Fafternoon, though staying largely dry
OL,9,Facross the region. Some rain during
OL,10,Fthe evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FPatchy frost initially on Thursday,
OL,14,Fbut then fine with some sunshine.
OL,15,FTurning unsettled over the Easter
OL,16,Fweekend with showers or longer spells
OL,17,Fof rain. Some strong and gusty winds
OL,18,Ftoo.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
